summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a deed for street purposes, an easement for street purposes, and an easement for signal loop detector in portions of Block 16, University Park Addition to the City of Seattle, Block 1, Brooklyn Addition to Seattle, and the Northwest Quarter of Section 16, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W.M., laying off Northeast 45th Street and 15th Avenue Northeast and assigning jurisdiction thereof (N.E. 45th T.I.B.; RW 8802).
